OL,3,CFuneral fundraiser for three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered off Brighton beach launched
OL,6,FA fundraising appeal has been launched
OL,7,Ffollowing the deaths of three sisters
OL,8,Fwho were recovered off Brighton beach
OL,9,Fto give them "the loving and dignified
OL,10,Ffarewell they deserve".
OL,12,FEmergency services were called after
OL,13,Fconcerns were raised for a person's
OL,14,Fwelfare at around 5.45am on May 13,
OL,15,Fbefore three bodies were pulled from
OL,16,Fthe water near Madeira Drive.
OL,18,FThe women have been named by Sussex
OL,19,FPolice as Jane Adetoro, 36, Christina
OL,20,FWalters, 32 and Rebecca Walters, 31,
OL,21,Ffrom the Uxbridge area of London.
OL,26,@qD@NOUrD@VO]
