CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779393955
OL,3,CFuneral fundraiser for three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered off Brighton beach launched
OL,6,FIn a statement made by their father
OL,7,FJoseph on Wednesday, he said there are
OL,8,Fdays when the grief feels "unbearable"
OL,9,Fbut he holds onto the memories they
OL,10,Fshared and "the bond that death can
OL,11,Fnever take away".
OL,13,FA GoFundMe page has been set up aiming
OL,14,Fto raise #18,000 for their funeral
OL,15,Fcosts.
OL,17,FFundraiser organiser Adesoji Adetoro
OL,18,Fwrote that it was set up on behalf of
OL,19,Fhis brother Joseph and the family,
OL,20,Fadding that they are struggling to
OL,21,Fcome to terms with what has happened.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@fO]rD@LOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
