PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779393955
OL,3,CFuneral fundraiser for three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered off Brighton beach launched
OL,6,F"No parent should ever have to bury
OL,7,Ftheir child, let alone all three," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"While trying to process this
OL,11,Funimaginable tragedy, my brother is
OL,12,Fnow also faced with the heartbreaking
OL,13,Ftask of arranging three funerals.
OL,15,F"As a family, we simply want to give
OL,16,Fthe girls the loving and dignified
OL,17,Ffarewell they deserve."
OL,19,FSince the fundraiser was launched more
OL,20,Fthan #3,000 has been donated.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@bO]rD@AOUwD@AOUyD@WO]
