OL,3,CFuneral fundraiser for three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered off Brighton beach launched
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Joseph paid tribute to
OL,7,Fhis daughters as his joy and strength,
OL,8,Fand "the beautiful light that filled
OL,9,Four family with happiness and love."
OL,11,F"Each of you was unique and precious
OL,12,Fin your own special way. Your smiles
OL,13,Fbrightened dark days, your laughter
OL,14,Fbrought comfort, and your presence
OL,15,Fmade life more meaningful," he said.
OL,26,@pD@EOUqD@dO]sD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
