PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779393955
OL,3,CFuneral fundraiser for three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered off Brighton beach launched
OL,6,FSussex Police have said there is no
OL,7,Fevidence to suggest criminality or
OL,8,Fthat anyone else was involved, but
OL,9,Fspecialist detectives are working to
OL,10,Fgather the full facts and
OL,11,Fcircumstances around their deaths.
OL,13,FHundreds of hours of CCTV footage have
OL,14,Fbeen reviewed and inquiries made to
OL,15,Fbusinesses and properties around the
OL,16,Fbeach area to try to track the women's
OL,17,Flast movements, the force said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
