PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779393955
OL,3,CFuneral fundraiser for three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered off Brighton beach launched
OL,6,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,7,Fcome forward, particularly anyone who
OL,8,Fsaw the sisters around the Madeira
OL,9,FDrive area between 10pm on May 12 and
OL,10,F5.30am May 13.
OL,12,FChief Superintendent Adam Hays has
OL,13,Fsaid the force "will leave no stone
OL,14,Funturned" in the investigation to
OL,15,Funderstand what led to the "tragic
OL,16,Fevents of that Wednesday morning".
OL,26,@uD@POUvD@IO]wD@\OUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
