PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779393955
OL,3,CFuneral fundraiser for three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered off Brighton beach launched
OL,6,FAfter the women were named, Brighton
OL,7,Fand Hove City Council leader Bella
OL,8,FSankey said to learn the women were
OL,9,Fsisters "makes this troubling
OL,10,Fsituation even more heartbreaking".
OL,12,F"My heart goes out their family and
OL,13,Ftheir friends," she said.
OL,15,F"Their grief and suffering must feel
OL,16,Foverwhelming, I hope that they have
OL,17,Fsupport in this worst of times.
OL,19,F"Brighton & Hove is grieving too and I
OL,20,Fwould like to again send them our
OL,21,Fdeepest condolences, and our love."
OL,26,@qD@IOUrD@bO]tD@AOUuD@OO]wD@AOU{D@AOU}D@
